# Integrate Turnitin Similarity for similarity check

If you have purchased Turnitin Similarity, you can now choose to integrate
this similarity checking solution with MaivenPoint system to enhance the value
of your investments. You can go to the **Settings** > **Turnitin** page to
provide the Turnitin URL and core API key to enable the integration.
